---
title: Spiced Beef Pilau with peas and yoghurt
description: This beef and rice pilau is lightly spiced for just the faintest hint of heat. It's also infused with a rich and fruity chutney for sweetness and depth of flavour that is sure to make this dish a dinnertime hit!
